Log:
  Fix icewm's buggy use of iconv which causes it to fail on 10.x.

  PR:		ports/182307
  Submitted by:	Wolfgang Zenker <wolfgang@lyxys.ka.sub.org> (incl. patch and testing)
  PR:		ports/183626
